-- BOE’s Posen Sees Case for 75B Pounds In Stimulus
-- B y   J e n n i f e r   R y a n   a n d   A n d r e a   C a t h e r w o o d
-- 2012-02-02T16:47:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-02/boe-s-posen-sees-case-for-75b-pounds-in-stimulus.html
Bank of England  policy makerAdam Posen said there is an argument for policy makers to increase
their bond-purchase program by another 75 billion pounds.  “75 billion was a good slug last time and there’s a case
to do it again,” he said in an interview on Bloomberg
Television today in London.  To contact the reporter on this story:
